title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1992-03-16

taper: Recording by Dave Brotman & Jeff Metchick

Set I
Let The Good Times Roll
Feel Like A Stranger

C.C. Rider >

Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar

Bruce Hornsby - Piano, Accordion
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
